snippet.title: DIY Everyday
snippet.description:
Welcome everyone! DIY Everyday is your beauty academy, one day - one tutorial. Here you can find hairstyle tutorials with long hair, bob haircuts also pixie cut. We love doing medium hair videos. Professionals will show you different hair hacks! And you will know all hair colour trends! Last time we love wedding hairstyles 💘
........................................................................................................

Our channel is made possible from talented, creative and amazing hairstylists from around the world! If you have an incredible video you want to see featured on our channel, send us an email along with a link to your profile to credit!
Thanks for watching!
